      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STREET SIXTY SIX (8) turned spotting a big start finishing fifth (24.39) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Can make amends. REBEL THINKER (5) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (23.76) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Comes through a solid form race last start. Expected to run well. SOUTH OF HEAVEN (2) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Has been in the money the last three starts, the latest when second (22.81) at Geelong. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Overdue and is among the main hopes. BLACK STATESMAN (1) can sneak into the finish.",
